+# AGENTS.md
+
+## Project
+**WellData Month-1 PIP demo**
+
+## Goals
+- Build a simple participant-facing demo.
+- Provide a timeline of questionnaire sessions.
+- Include a score explainability panel.
+- Show preventive action recommendations.
+
+## Constraints
+- Keep the UX very simple.
+- No backend integration yet.
+- Do **not** implement DPoP or UMA.
+- Do **not** implement pod write/read.
+- Focus on visible demo functionality.
+
+## Working Style
+- Prefer small, modular files.
+- Create small incremental commits.
+- Keep code readable and minimal.
